snippet.title: Puzzlecar [STEAM TRAILER]
snippet.description:
A minimalist and relaxing experience. Challenge yourself to move pieces to assemble a safe path for your car and collect all the items on the way, while listening to a relaxing soundtrack in a totally minimalist environment.

Gamepage:
https://www.risingmoongames.com/our-games/puzzlecar
